<title>CUSTOMIZATION</title>
<simpara><emphasis role="strong">awesome</emphasis> is customized by creating a custom <emphasis>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/awesome/rc.lua</emphasis> file.</simpara>
</refsect1>
